{"tid":1357744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好心你地on9少陣","createTime":"2019-07-23T19:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T20:02:23.000Z","uid":170218,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6639404c6013146fb174826fad1bc07ca76bbb43","tid":1357744,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:12:47.000Z","msg":"好心你地咁大個人就唔好再咁on9玩分化<br />\n我係元朗人 但係同時我發夢都去咗中上環<br />\n元朗係重要 但同樣地中上環都重要<br />\n義士係重要 但同樣地俾人打嘅無辜市民都重要<br />\n根本無需要比較<br />\n到底比較黎做咩啫？？有咩意思啫？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再同我提condom 呢度冇一個人係condom<br />\n講左10鳩幾萬次唔好玩分化</span></span><br />\n結果成班小學雞係咁喺度玩 <br />\n可以Focus返係個重點未？？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家係要集中返係五大訴求到</span></span><br />\n係要集中返下一步應該點做<br />\n727見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddd162928d97bb772b6c9da639a86cb462e8852","tid":1357744,"uid":285536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:13:21.000Z","msg":"和理非 加自衛<br />\n宜家何君堯重要死亡恐嚇朱凱迪！？<br />\n反白色恐怖！還我免於恐懼的自由<br />\n反警黑元朗大遊行！<br />\n一齊黎一齊走 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"670ece41cf2702b693d4e646f620ad937bc7d35b","tid":1357744,"uid":260895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:13:45.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9847ab3cca2076b48f42b9980838941a10c2eb","tid":1357744,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:17:22.000Z","msg":"推到你地班分化撚見到"},{"pid":"553c5b657bd489e718b10235e1b6949d07e31cac","tid":1357744,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d191c81c81ecd903050ce75db8f9081af83e281a","tid":1357744,"uid":170218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:22:34.000Z","msg":"推呀！！"},{"pid":"4248aa75d299cf56751375a89b257f3e9468be5d","tid":1357744,"uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc